b1:0 Global Async event direction
00 - radarSS to MSS 01 - radarSS to HOST

[1.] CPU_FAULT [2.] ESM_FAULT [3.] ANALOG_FAULT
All other ASYNC_EVENTs are sent to the subsystem which issues the API
